{
  "stem": "7860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And many time, I used to land jobs like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One cow, a peasant would have on a rope to graze the cow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And till-- they couldn't last too long, I was doing a good job because I used to steal potatoes from other people's fields and feed the cow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to bring home the cow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had lots of milk in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the peasant used to praise me how good I am but he'd send me home anyways for his safety.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we get a birth certificate-- well, I couldn't produce no birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I used to go on and beg again until I found more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, my mother seen that everybody's dying in the ghetto, amongst them my father, and my middle brother Abraham.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- Do you remember the circumstances around the death of your father and brother?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father died of hunger in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- middle of the night, he woke us up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, chase him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came to get me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whoever he was referring to, my mother said go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stop talking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We woke up in the morning, he was dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all slept in the same bed-- keep ourself warm, all five of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the morning, the man used to pass by, pick up the bodies, and picked, and took-- my mother summoned them to come down and drag the body of my father out and dumped him on top of the wagon with all the other bodies.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then my mother snuck out of the ghetto with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she asked the caregiver, Jewish man, elderly Jewish man-- maybe he wasn't as old as he looked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where is my father?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
